body:
Updated items are in sync with being prepared 2018 HCAL MC conditions update for 10_1_X : 
(1) HcalChannelQuality : removal of (non-instrumented)  |ieta|=18 depth=1 readouts;
(2) HcalGains: increasing gain (GeV/fC) for QIE11 channels, using average 2017 HEP17 value;
(3) HcalSiPMParameters: bringing fC/p.e. in synch with the actual "in situ" value(s).

Changes affect workflows, which use hardcode HCAL conditions: Run3 (HB and HE) and Phase 2 (HB). 
The changes are supposed to be quite small.
